Documentation of Scripts & Database:

Everything is available under the http://students.washington.edu/cyc025/db/ directory. 
so it would be http://students.washington.edu/cyc025/db/[file name]

Database Schema:

		$table = "CREATE TABLE pizza_order (
		id INT(6) UNSIGNED PRIMARY KEY, 
		item VARCHAR(45) NOT NULL,
		reg_date TIMESTAMP,
		quantity INT(5),
		size VARCHAR(20),
		detail VARCHAR(200),
		price DOUBLE(5,3) NOT NULL,
		completed TINYINT(1))"

===========================================================

display.php

Display main page for all orders.

===========================================================

manage.php  

Allow shop owners to manage orders by either confirm them or cancel them.

===========================================================

post_data.php 

Post order data to database.

===========================================================

post_name.php

Post name audio file to database.

===========================================================

post_address.php

Post address audio file to database.

===========================================================

maxorder.php

Return current maximum order.

===========================================================

insert.php

Connector with database, to post data into database.

===========================================================

upload.php

Allow admin to directly add audio files.

===========================================================

form.html

Allow admin to directly add orders.

===========================================================

